<title>컴퓨존</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=euc-kr">
<link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="/css/font.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<style>
body { background:#F9F9F9; font-family:Noto-R;}
#wrap { width:100%; }
.error_wrap { width:600px; height: calc(100vh - 96px); margin:0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;}
.error_wrap span { width:146px; height:30px; display:inline-block; background:url(//image5.compuzone.co.kr/img/images/main/logo.gif) left bottom no-repeat; background-size:146px auto; padding-top: 80px;}
.error_wrap p { text-align:center; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:-1px; color:#666; line-height:1.54em; }
.error_wrap .btn {width: 100%; height: 52px; border-radius: 10px; display:inline-block; border:#D8D8D8 1px solid;margin:40px 0 0 0; color:#1A1A1A; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:-1px; font-size:18px; line-height: 52px;}
.error_wrap .btn > p {color:#1A1A1A; text-decoration:none; font-size:18px; line-height: 52px; font-family:Noto-M; }
.error_box {padding:80px 0 40px; text-align:center;}
.error_copyright {width: 100%; height: 96px; border-top: 1px solid #D8D8D8; box-sizing: border-box;}

/* 코미동영상 */
.comi160 {width:160px; height:160px; margin:0 auto;}
.comivideo {width:100%;}

</style>
<body>
<!--############### main start(전체) ###############-->

<div id="wrap">
	<div class="error_wrap">
        <a href="../main/main.htm"><span></span></a>
        <div class="error_box">
            <div class="comi160">
                <video class="comivideo" src="//image5.compuzone.co.kr/img/images/comi/comi_question.webm" muted autoplay playsinline loop></video>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:24px; font-weight: bold; color:#1a1a1a; letter-spacing:-0.6px; margin:20px 0 10px;">
                요청하신 페이지에 연결할 수 없습니다.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #949494; letter-spacing: -0.38px; " >
                입력한 주소가 잘못 되었거나 사용이 일시중단 되었습니다.<br>
                확인 후 다시 이용해 주세요.
            </p>
            <a href="../main/main.htm" class="btn"><p>컴퓨존 메인으로</p></a>
        </div>
	</div>
	<div class="error_copyright">
		<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #949494; line-height: 94px;">
			COPYRIGHTⓒ COMPUZONE ALL RIGHTS RESERVED
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

<!--############### main start(전체) ###############-->
</body>
</html>